{"tid":1657552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何君堯「洋腸」論涉歧視　平機會指非跟進範圍","createTime":"2019-10-16T06:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T08:15:06.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1008ac765f888a2db10e45b0c85778b26d9ab558","tid":1657552,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯昨日(15日)在內委會會議內，指議員毛孟靜「食慣洋腸嗰啲人佢可能自己侮辱自己」，被轟涉及性別歧視、性騷擾、種族歧視。平等機會委員會主席朱敏健今早(16日)在電台節目表示，平機會在短時間內收到約30宗相關的查詢，但個案並非平機會可跟進範圍。朱續指，由於有關語句與性騷擾相關，為了維護被性騷擾人士，平機會於是發出聲明。<br />\n另外，朱指自6月中起，平機會接收了超過300宗有關警方執法的查詢，主要是《性別歧視條例》下懷疑性騷擾的個案，例如有人提出，警方對示威者搜身時懷疑作出不當行為的指控。"},{"pid":"bb3e587086004f8e881caaa9fd46bf5c1e4bbb81","tid":1657552,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"77da2e57eea7559a256038bbbe8a055f1033c02c","tid":1657552,"uid":290118,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:51:49.000Z","msg":"執柒咗佢啦"},{"pid":"e41299ecb2ce3879990fc0d6d2bcb89acf017950","tid":1657552,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:56:47.000Z","msg":"胡志偉: 林鄭係八婆<br />\n平機會即時跟進"},{"pid":"5c3619ca4914958eb8d29f38b9d249abc16b957f","tid":1657552,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:57:44.000Z","msg":"事撚但啦。都無期望架啦"},{"pid":"44b9bb63d4e3c738a5105c1b8f7535e95730d5f3","tid":1657552,"uid":246165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e41299ecb2ce3879990fc0d6d2bcb89acf017950","tid":1657552,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:56:47.000Z","msg":"胡志偉: 林鄭係八婆<br />\n平機會即時跟進"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"林鄭：平機會都係我嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點同我鬥呀"},{"pid":"6e5a1c06372b1006